 in the domain of data-intensive\nsystems and suggests open research directions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Mar 2022 09:55:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 25 Nov 2022 17:05:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2023 11:53:39 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2023 05:14:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-08"}
