re and\ntechnosignature searches can complement and supplement each other and how\nmethods of technosignature search, including old ideas from SETI, can inform\nthe search for biosignatures and life generally.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Mar 2022 11:48:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-22"}
